OL,3,CMan who held people hostage at knife-
OL,4,Cpoint jailed
OL,6,FA man who held people hostage at knife-
OL,7,Fpoint in North Yorkshire has been
OL,8,Fjailed.
OL,10,FJordan Kelly, 23, was sentenced to
OL,11,Ffour years after assaulting two
OL,12,Fpeople, as well as a police officer
OL,13,Fwho came to their aid.
OL,15,FThe incident happened during the early
OL,16,Fhours of Saturday 9 September 2023.
