OL,3,CMan who held people hostage at knife-
OL,4,Cpoint jailed
OL,6,FA woman contacted Cleveland Police
OL,7,Fwith concerns for the welfare of a man
OL,8,F- however, the man then returned to an
OL,9,Faddress in Yarm, forcing himself into
OL,10,Fthe property.
OL,12,FIt was reported that Kelly had a
OL,13,Fknife. He assaulted a woman, and was
OL,14,Ffighting with others in the address.
OL,16,FWhen police arrived at the scene, and
OL,17,Fattempted to remove Kelly, he became
OL,18,Faggressive towards the officers,
OL,19,Fpushing one against the wall and
OL,20,Ftrying to kick him.
