OL,3,CMan who held people hostage at knife-
OL,4,Cpoint jailed
OL,6,FThe group of people who were present
OL,7,Ftold police Kelly had held them
OL,8,Fhostage while threatening them with a
OL,9,Fknife. He had also made threats to
OL,10,Fkill one of the women and the man - as
OL,11,Fwell as himself.
OL,13,FKelly, from Seamer, North Yorkshire,
OL,14,Fwas sentenced at Teesside Crown Court
OL,15,Fat the end of March.
OL,17,FDetectives have welcomed the four-year
OL,18,Fsentence given to Kelly, saying it
OL,19,F"reflects the gravity of the crimes"
OL,20,Fhe had committed.
