OL,6,F"This was a case involving an
OL,7,Funprovoked attack on multiple victims
OL,8,Fand was undoubtedly terrifying for
OL,9,Fthem and for the officers who came to
OL,10,Fhelp them.
OL,12,F"The victims had the strength and
OL,13,Fcourage to tell police exactly what
OL,14,Fhad happened and we are grateful for
OL,15,Fthis," Temporary Detective Constable
OL,16,FSamantha Finlayson, of Cleveland
OL,17,FPolice's Domestic Abuse Unit, had said.
